---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Christopher Klint | Engineering Leader & Tech Speaker" description="Christopher Klint is a Stockholm-based engineering leader and tech speaker, specializing in scalable platforms, cloud-native architecture, and building high-performance engineering teams.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
        Christopher Klint
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        Engineering Leader & Tech Speaker
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        Strategic engineering leader based in Stockholm, Sweden. I specialize in building scalable platforms, driving product strategy, and growing high-performance engineering teams. Currently a Staff Engineer at <a href="https://telnesstech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Telness Tech</a>, working on cloud-based telecom infrastructure that powers mobile operators worldwide.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">What I do</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Platform engineering:</strong> Designing APIs and architecting end-to-end product capabilities, increasing integration speed with network operators by 80%.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Team building:</strong> Scaled engineering teams from 10 to 50+, with a track record of mentoring developers and reducing onboarding time to under 20 days. Awarded Role Model of the Year two consecutive years.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Product strategy:</strong> Developed technology roadmaps aligned with executive vision, enabling new revenue streams and accelerating product launches by 75%.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Cloud optimization:</strong> Reduced cloud infrastructure costs by 50% through strategic right-sizing, logging optimizations, and efficient CI/CD workflows.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Speaking & podcasts</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          I regularly speak about engineering leadership, building inclusive teams, and effective collaboration. Recent appearances include:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Women in Tech Sweden</strong> &mdash; Panel on feedback culture and delivering it effectively (Regatta 2023)</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">EqualIT Podcast</strong> &mdash; Building high-performing inclusive teams through trust and vulnerability</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">The Live Series (Amicus)</strong> &mdash; Effective collaboration in tech teams, alongside engineers from Banked, Develop Diverse, and Miro</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Evolution Recruitment</strong> &mdash; Leadership and building scalable engineering cultures</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          Open to speaking at events, conferences, and podcasts. <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">Get in touch</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Technical expertise</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["TypeScript", "Go", "React", "Next.js", "Node.js", "GraphQL", "REST APIs", "AWS", "Azure", "Google Cloud", "Microservices", "CI/CD", "PostgreSQL", "Docker"].map((skill) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">{skill}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-6">
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary px-6 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
        >
          About Me
        </a>
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-6 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
        >
          Read the Blog
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-6 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
